#猎豹守护 
灵猴和猎豹切换
```
/run local i,x=1,0 while UnitBuff("player",i) do if UnitBuff("player",i)=="Interface\\Icons\\Ability_Hunter_AspectOfTheMonkey" then x=1 end i=i+1 end if x==0 then CastSpellByName("灵猴守护") else CastSpellByName("猎豹守护")end
```
#一键守护 MU(Y+)
移动中，身边8码内没有敌人且身上没有猎豹守护或者豹群守护就使用猎豹守护；如果目标是未死亡的敌对目标且距离大于8码，切换雄鹰守护；距离小于8码且敌人目标是你使用灵猴守护；否则使用孤狼守护战输出
/cast [moving,enemynum:dst8=0,nomybuff:猎豹守护/豹群守护]猎豹守护;[harm,nodead,distance:>=8,nomybuff:雄鹰守护]雄鹰守护;
/cast [harm,nodead,distance:<8,targeting:player,nomybuff:灵猴守护]灵猴守护;[harm,nodead,distance:<8,notargeting:player,nomybuff:孤狼守护]孤狼守护


#钉刺T(不绑定，一键宏开关)
```
/script class=UnitClass("target") c=CastSpellByName; if UnitIsPlayer("target") and ((class=="Rogue") or (class=="Warrior")) then c("毒蝎钉刺") elseif UnitIsPlayer("target") or UnitName("target")=="莫阿姆" then c("蝰蛇钉刺") else c("毒蛇钉刺"); end
```

#一键宏多功能MD(RT)
利用GCD，优先猎人印记和Pet攻击，然后进入兽王猎循环，技能在CAT中配置。(hbdps优先自动射击，宏里面先写印记)。目标交互，打开低吼
```
/run if UnitHealth("target")==0 and UnitExists("target") then ClearTarget(); end
/run if GetUnitName("target")==nil then TargetNearestEnemy(); end
/run local i,x=1,0 while UnitDebuff("target",i) do if UnitDebuff("target",i)=="Interface\\Icons\\Ability_Hunter_SniperShot" then x=1 end i=i+1 end if x==0 then CastSpellByName("猎人印记") end
/script PetAttack()
/ru﻿n local i,g=1,0 while GetSpellName(i,"pet") do if GetSpellName(i,"pet")=="低吼" then g=i end i=i+1 end local _,y = GetSpellAutocast(g,"pet") if not y then ToggleSpellAutocast(g,"pet") end
/hbdps
/run Interact(0)
/run ToggleSheath()
```

